                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-39-off228 t18280410-39-crimeloc231"></join>, and left my basket on the ground, about twenty yards from where I was serving a customer; I had lost bread two or three days running, and told the constable to watch; I saw him collar the prisoner, with two loaves under his arm - I am certain they are master's.</p>
